"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"![One day, technology might allow us to teleport through time and revisit our fondest memories. This piece depicts what that technology might look like.](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/L9xJhxfwqQpGxBWKeAE5I.png?height=1907&width=2667)\\n\\nPicture this: You wake up one morning on Pluto reminiscing about the time you visited Paris (a place that unfortunately no longer exists). You *could* put on your VR headset and pull up a hyper-realistic render of Paris, but today you don’t want to. Today, you want to go to the Paris that *you* remember. Today, you want to engage with reality, not the metaverse.\\n\\nYou hop into your spaceship and fly over to your Space Shelf located a few thousand miles away from Mars. You approach the portal containing the Eiffel Tower (located in row 13, column 22). After passing through the portal, you land your spaceship in the Champ de Mars and relive the Paris you so vividly remember. The portal does not bend space-time and it does not allow you to change your memory in any way, but it does allow you to relive defining life moments (good or bad, it’s your choice) with crystal clarity. Because after all, there’s no camera or VR technology that could compete with the world you’ve seen and perceived with your own eyes.\\n\\n![The Paris Portal (the last column of the second row)](https://images.mirror-media.xyz/publication-images/9tTvCUgbQAxziwUVu0NPp.png?height=1906&width=2668)\\n\\n\",\"timestamp\":1637769895,\"title\":\"Space Shelf of Memory Portals (circa 15,000 AD)\"},\"digest\":\"mB_kPLajMu_waUK9T1q5yl8nxkNStNulOqyDgXnBEZs\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0xBC8D2B776794F9DA950ba7096bF4A9Ac9368eC3e\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"NrLDaYU7_CrZGBPhixC0TpzeXhfFLUnp1fQjlnyPoZ8\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"3ih6voHfSZC8C-tRpyo4L0lxupuDtjaK_PfBzoa4O6Q\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"77_MQbAhIeRTmCKv5Ee0hfyWzIrelhvOps_CETXzYIBE5zYTlanEk7yD8KKKl7WdK70bxZjTdfwa5AHyIHCrWg\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xe416d4cc57dac4195f2ab3abee351ee9cb6d41879783fc4e28cc1f32a12b40640b5df775f75e87bd62aae60c60ba736261efc147d656375fd2da98caabf505a71b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"NrLDaYU7_CrZGBPhixC0TpzeXhfFLUnp1fQjlnyPoZ8\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"3ih6voHfSZC8C-tRpyo4L0lxupuDtjaK_PfBzoa4O6Q\\\"}\",\"algorithm\":{\"name\":\"ECDSA\",\"hash\":\"SHA-256\"}},\"nft\":{},\"version\":\"12-21-2020\",\"originalDigest\":\"mB_kPLajMu_waUK9T1q5yl8nxkNStNulOqyDgXnBEZs\"}"